# spiral.tg
# An expanding square spiral using a variable to grow each side.
#
# 'set n <val>' assigns a value.
# '(n + 2)' is parenthesised arithmetic.
# The slight offset from 90 degrees (89) stops the lines from
# exactly overlapping each other, creating the spiral effect.

pen 1
set n 5
dotimes 80 {
    forward n
    turn 89
    set n (n + 2)
}
